---
syntax: bash
tags:
- elixir
- phoenix
---

# To install Phoenix tooling
mix archive.install hex phx_new

# To display current hex version installed
mix phx.new -v

# To create a new project with default components and naming conventions
mix phx.new hello_world

# To create an app backed by sqlite as the datastore
mix phx.new --database sqlite3 my_app

